    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_es.00292.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place"><handShift rend="printed"/>Superintendent's Office.<ptr
                            target="loc.07222_n1"/><lb/>ASYLUM FOR THE INSANE<lb/>LONDON.<lb/>
                        ONTARIO<lb/>London, Ont.,</name>
                    <date when="1888-08-11" rend="right"><handShift rend="manuscript"/>11 Aug
                            <handShift rend="printed"/>188<handShift rend="manuscript"/>8</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>I have your card of 9th Harkness<ptr target="n4278"/> has been here a couple of days
                we put in the time quietly and pleasantly together chatting, driving, &#38;c &#38;c.
                We have been friends now 30 years. He will stay till middle of next week. Weather
                keeps pleasant&#8212;we have had plenty of rain &#38; the trees &#38; grass are very
                green. Mrs Bucke<ptr target="n4273"/> still away and the house quiet&#8212;not to
                say dull. We have whist in the evening often and we all enjoy it&#8212;No news.</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Love to you</salute>
                <signed rend="right">RM Bucke</signed>
            </closer>
